{"thi-ap34:0.1":"Theriapadana ","thi-ap34:0.2":"Khattiyavagga ","thi-ap34:0.3":"4 Singalamatutheriapadana ","thi-ap34:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","thi-ap34:1.2":"sabbadhammana paragu; ","thi-ap34:1.3":"Ito satasahassamhi, ","thi-ap34:1.4":"kappe uppajji nayako. ","thi-ap34:2.1":"Tadaham hamsavatiyam, ","thi-ap34:2.2":"jatamaccakule ahum; ","thi-ap34:2.3":"Nanaratanapajjote, ","thi-ap34:2.4":"iddhe phite mahaddhane. ","thi-ap34:3.1":"Pituna saha gantvana, ","thi-ap34:3.2":"mahajanapurakkhata; ","thi-ap34:3.3":"Dhammam buddhassa sutvana, ","thi-ap34:3.4":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","thi-ap34:4.1":"Pabbajitvana kayena, ","thi-ap34:4.2":"papakammam vivajjayim; ","thi-ap34:4.3":"Vaciduccaritam hitva, ","thi-ap34:4.4":"ajivam parisodhayim. ","thi-ap34:5.1":"Buddhe pasanna dhamme ca, ","thi-ap34:5.2":"sanghe ca tibbagarava; ","thi-ap34:5.3":"Saddhammassavane yutta, ","thi-ap34:5.4":"buddhadassanalalasa. ","thi-ap34:6.1":"Aggam saddhadhimuttanam, ","thi-ap34:6.2":"assosim bhikkhunim tada; ","thi-ap34:6.3":"Tam thanam patthayitvana, ","thi-ap34:6.4":"tisso sikkha apurayim. ","thi-ap34:7.1":"Tato mam sugato aha, ","thi-ap34:7.2":"karunanugatasayo; ","thi-ap34:7.3":"‘Yassa saddha tathagate, ","thi-ap34:7.4":"acala suppatitthita; ","thi-ap34:7.5":"Silanca yassa kalyanam, ","thi-ap34:7.6":"ariyakantam pasamsitam. ","thi-ap34:8.1":"Sanghe pasado yassatthi, ","thi-ap34:8.2":"ujubhutanca dassanam; ","thi-ap34:8.3":"Adaliddoti tam ahu, ","thi-ap34:8.4":"amogham tassa jivitam. ","thi-ap34:9.1":"Tasma saddhanca silanca, ","thi-ap34:9.2":"pasadam dhammadassanam; ","thi-ap34:9.3":"Anuyunjetha medhavi, ","thi-ap34:9.4":"saram buddhana sasanam’. ","thi-ap34:10.1":"Tam sutvaham pamudita, ","thi-ap34:10.2":"apucchim panidhim mama; ","thi-ap34:10.3":"Tada anomo amito, ","thi-ap34:10.4":"byakarittha vinayako; ","thi-ap34:10.5":"‘Buddhe pasanna kalyani, ","thi-ap34:10.6":"lacchase tam supatthitam. ","thi-ap34:11.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","thi-ap34:11.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","thi-ap34:11.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","thi-ap34:11.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","thi-ap34:12.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayada, ","thi-ap34:12.2":"orasa dhammanimmita; ","thi-ap34:12.3":"Singalakassa matati, ","thi-ap34:12.4":"hessati satthu savika’. ","thi-ap34:13.1":"Tam sutva mudita hutva, ","thi-ap34:13.2":"yavajivam tada jinam; ","thi-ap34:13.3":"Mettacitta paricarim, ","thi-ap34:13.4":"patipattihi nayakam. ","thi-ap34:14.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","thi-ap34:14.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","thi-ap34:14.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","thi-ap34:14.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","thi-ap34:15.1":"Pacchime ca bhave dani, ","thi-ap34:15.2":"giribbajapuruttame; ","thi-ap34:15.3":"Jata setthikule phite, ","thi-ap34:15.4":"maharatanasancaye. ","thi-ap34:16.1":"Putto singalako nama, ","thi-ap34:16.2":"mamasi vipathe rato; ","thi-ap34:16.3":"Ditthigahanapakkhando, ","thi-ap34:16.4":"disapujanatapparo. ","thi-ap34:17.1":"Nanadisa namassantam, ","thi-ap34:17.2":"pindaya nagaram vajam; ","thi-ap34:17.3":"Tam disva ovadi buddho, ","thi-ap34:17.4":"magge thatva vinayako. ","thi-ap34:18.1":"Tassa desayato dhammam, ","thi-ap34:18.2":"panado vimhayo ahu; ","thi-ap34:18.3":"Dvekotinaranarinam, ","thi-ap34:18.4":"dhammabhisamayo ahu. ","thi-ap34:19.1":"Tadaham parisam gantva, ","thi-ap34:19.2":"sutva sugatabhasitam; ","thi-ap34:19.3":"Sotapattiphalam patta, ","thi-ap34:19.4":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","thi-ap34:20.1":"Na cireneva kalena, ","thi-ap34:20.2":"buddhadassanalalasa; ","thi-ap34:20.3":"Anussatim tam bhavetva, ","thi-ap34:20.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","thi-ap34:21.1":"Dassanatthaya buddhassa, ","thi-ap34:21.2":"sabbada ca vajamaham; ","thi-ap34:21.3":"Atittayeva passami, ","thi-ap34:21.4":"rupam nayananandanam. ","thi-ap34:22.1":"Sabbaparamisambhutam, ","thi-ap34:22.2":"lakkhinilayanam varam; ","thi-ap34:22.3":"Rupam sabbasubhakinnam, ","thi-ap34:22.4":"atitta viharamaham. ","thi-ap34:23.1":"Jino tasmim gune tuttho, ","thi-ap34:23.2":"etadagge thapesi mam; ","thi-ap34:23.3":"‘Singalakassa ya mata, ","thi-ap34:23.4":"agga saddhadhimuttika’. ","thi-ap34:24.1":"Iddhisu ca vasi homi, ","thi-ap34:24.2":"dibbaya sotadhatuya; ","thi-ap34:24.3":"Cetopariyananassa, ","thi-ap34:24.4":"vasi homi mahamuni. ","thi-ap34:25.1":"Pubbenivasam janami, ","thi-ap34:25.2":"dibbacakkhu visodhitam; ","thi-ap34:25.3":"Sabbasava parikkhina, ","thi-ap34:25.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","thi-ap34:26.1":"Atthadhammaniruttisu, ","thi-ap34:26.2":"patibhane tatheva ca; ","thi-ap34:26.3":"Nanam mama mahavira, ","thi-ap34:26.4":"uppannam tava santike. ","thi-ap34:27.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","thi-ap34:27.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap34:27.3":"viharami anasava. ","thi-ap34:28.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","thi-ap34:28.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap34:28.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thi-ap34:29.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","thi-ap34:29.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap34:29.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","thi-ap34:30.1":"Ittham sudam singalamata bhikkhuni ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","thi-ap34:31.1":"Singalamatutheriyapadanam catuttham. "}